Moseley Securities Corp said Howard Bergresigned as chairman and chief executive officer.    It said Frederick S. Moseley III assumed the position ofchairman. In other management changes, Omar Kassem was namedvice chairman and chief executive officer, and JamesWolitarsky, executive vice president and chief financialofficer, was appointed president and chief operating officer.    The company also said it named a Management Committeeconsisting of Wolitarsky and six executive vice presidents. Reuter&#3;